{"tid":457823,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"TVB奇招救收視！11月復播《歡樂今宵》","createTime":"2017-11-04T09:03:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-12T06:08:41.000Z","uid":14730,"like":8,"dislike":179,"uniUserReply":99,"replies":[{"pid":"585b858719d0bf47ad3957cf9484039ae9edd016","tid":457823,"uid":14730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T09:03:11.000Z","msg":"「歡歡樂樂，笑笑談談我哋齊齊陪伴你！」這一句，相信不少香港人都非常深刻。《歡樂今宵》1967年開播至1994年，陪伴著不少人成長，亦成為最長壽的綜藝節目。節目單元多元化，除了唱歌、舞蹈表演外，更有專訪、短劇等形式，不少藝人都會參與節目的演出，非常熱鬧。而節目所用的題材通常都比較貼地，所以非常受觀眾歡迎。<br />\n<br />\n最近無綫電視即將在十一月復播《歡樂今宵》，並命名為《我愛EYT》。汪明荃、曾志偉等人都大力支持，亦表示將會有大量藝人參演。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2AjfCWL\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2AjfCWL&d=gYuG1EsZJ%2F3sPoSh6ac4jKWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=cf4e9c17\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2AjfCWL</a>"},{"pid":"f47adeb7087cdc0a486d0e8cf1eb1d71a5b4e3b7","tid":457823,"uid":38988,"like":126,"dislike":2,"score":124,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T09:10:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">圍</span><span style=\"color: green;\">威</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">喂</span></span>"},{"pid":"63e212fc06390fc84acf21462c203778da49703b","tid":457823,"uid":18772,"like":84,"dislike":2,"score":82,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T09:10:54.000Z","msg":"估唔到咁快進入回憶既階段"},{"pid":"e743a9f939e5b111f11f1380dfbaade8798d5c5b","tid":457823,"uid":3369,"like":263,"dislike":2,"score":261,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T09:12:06.000Z","msg":"仆街，TVB真係亞視化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f55f86ccd3099f9c4c24ea72f1da9240680a2652","tid":457823,"uid":86587,"like":59,"dislike":2,"score":57,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T09:12:16.000Z","msg":"阿蛆條廢老又喺度獻世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48733fc84c4765a8902ac68698c0c92b93ead534","tid":457823,"uid":21249,"like":12,"dislike":2,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T09:27:48.0